Russell M. CARTER, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
IOWA DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL RESOURCES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-0087 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Plaintiff appeals the district court decision on his petition for declaratory judgment finding Iowa Code section 483A.24 (2016) is not unconstitutional. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
